undoubtedly the final exit from the Division into two separate and independent states. Against all odds, the Cyprus Problem seems to have come to its definitive end, with action following promises and a lot of good will from both communities, diplomats and politicians. This was that historic step of rejoining our country or more exactly of putting the government back in the hands of the European conscience, the guardian of the rule of law.

Thereafter, the search for convergence points of the two sides’ desires, habits, needs, intentions and objectives inevitably brought with it also many of the symbolic conventions of markets which up until then had remained distant and unknown. Meaning that while the 4 epoch-defining transitions through which we have lived always left us in the middle and the evolution of society happened parallel to all other social evolutions -if not in the front ranks- this one it happened in parallel to everyone else, with no master system or ideas of its own model, just like our population of babies learned to walk one step at a time with a gait of their own. Reaching much further than ever before.

How then to rise all the way to the historic objectives of the Republic of Cyprus, with the new resources at our command?

1. No longer being led by calculations and concerns of conflicted identity issues, we are now able to set the objectives of our planning upon the background of a Res Publica
